snippet.title: Cosmodread - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Cosmodread is a VR survival horror roguelike.
Get it here:
- https://store.steampowered.com/app/1256060/Cosmodread/
- https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3688751474502123

Trapped in a dying spaceship filled with horrors, you must find your way back to the safety of Earth. Cosmodread features a rich, immersive atmosphere that will make you forget about the world outside the headset.


More info: http://www.cosmodread.com/
